- https://github.com/apache/netbeans/issues/6074
- Add "Match Arm Arrow" as an alignment option
- Add/Fix unit tests

Example:
```php
match ($type1) {
    'integer', 'test' => 'test',
    'string' => match ($type2) {
        1, 2 => "test",
        3 => "test",
        4 => "test",
    },
    default => null,
};
```

Result:

```php
match ($type1) {
    'integer', 'test' => 'test',
    'string'          => match ($type2) {
        1, 2 => "test",
        3    => "test",
        4    => "test",
    },
    default           => null,
};
```
